Program: Great Lives
Title: The Man in the Iron Mask
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0076f5w
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 23 Jan 2015
Military historian Richard Holmes nominates the mysterious Man in the Iron Mask. With Humphrey Carpenter and John Noone. From May 2003. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? Show less